data.description: This spectacular home sits high on a hill with a beautiful view. Located just east of Mount Vernon sitting on just over 1 acre of land. This 3 bedroom, 3.5 bath home boosts 2,240 sqft. Entering the foyer you'll find a main level office, formal dining room, open kitchen/living room complete with a wood burning fireplace. Main level 1/2 bath & laundry room. Upstairs master bedroom with spacious walk in closet & bath. Bonus space & 2 additional bedrooms on the second level with full bath. Walk out lower level, full bathroom with walk in tile shower & potential additional bedroom & family room. Tons of storage space available in lower level. Exterior featuring vinyl siding/stone, covered front porch & 2 car garage.  Showings start 12/1/23.
